  <description><![CDATA[<p>Combining three contrasting regions from Lake Geneva in south-western Switzerland, via the Bernese Oberland and the GoldenPass Line to Germany's Lake Constance on the north-eastern border, with opportunity to visit some popular and lesser known UNESCO World Heritage Sites along the way - the Lavaux vineyards, Swiss Alps Jungfrau-Aletsch Jungfraujoch and monasteries of Reichenau and St. Gallen.</p>
<p> </p>
